description: Recording ID. Unique recording ID - a combination of media type, child ID, and month, e.g., video_41_12. See README or seedlings-nouns-codebook.csv for details.
Media type. See seedlings-nouns codebook for more information.
Subject ID. See seedlings-nouns codebook for more information.
Month ID. See seedlings-nouns codebook for more information.
Recording duration. Length of the audio recording file or the compiled video file rounded to the nearest second.
Listened time. The duration of top 4 (months 06-13) or top 3 (month 14-17) annotated hours rounded to the nearest second. For videos, identical to `duration_time`.

Surplus time. The time beyond top 4 (months 06-13) or top 3 (month 14-17) annotated hours that was annotated as well. For months 06-07, consists of the whole recording minus the top 4 regions and silence regions. For videos, it is zero.
